Class Phase

java.lang.Object
java.util.concurrent.FutureTask<V>
javafx.concurrent.Task<Void>
cotelab.dupfilefinder2.pipeline.Phase
All Implemented Interfaces:
QueueProcessor, Runnable, Future<Void>, RunnableFuture<Void>, javafx.concurrent.Worker<Void>, javafx.event.EventTarget
Direct Known Subclasses:
GroupByContentPhase, GroupByContentWorker, GroupBySizePhase, MatchingSubtreeIdentificationPhase, Pipeline, SubtreeSearchPhase
public abstract class Phase extends javafx.concurrent.Task<Void> implements QueueProcessor
A Task that may have child tasks that it manages. A tree of Phase objects may be created and managed as one.
